123
00:05:28,770 --> 00:05:30,190
Anyway, the point is,

124
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:33,629
if you mess with Chinese citizens for breaking
your laws,

125
00:05:33,629 --> 00:05:35,939
the Chinese Communist Party won’t hesitate
to

126
00:05:35,939 --> 00:05:39,330
break China’s laws to mess with your citizens.

127
00:05:39,330 --> 00:05:41,650
In fact, in addition to Michael Kovrig,

128
00:05:41,650 --> 00:05:44,440
Chinese authorities have also abducted, uh,

129
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:48,250
detained another Canadian citizen named Michael
Spavor.

130
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:50,289
If you’re a Canadian named Michael,

131
00:05:50,289 --> 00:05:52,499
maybe now is a good time to leave China.

132
00:05:52,499 --> 00:05:54,949
Spavor started a company in China that promotes

133
00:05:54,949 --> 00:05:57,620
